---
// Game landing page for The Wellspring
---

<html>
  <head>
    <title>The Wellspring | ephergent.com</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@900&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a1a 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #0a0a1a 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
        color: #e0e0e0;
      }
      .game-hero {
        font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        color: #0ff1ce;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff1ce88;
      }
      .tagline {
        color: #0ff1ce;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0ff1ce44;
      }
      .nav-link {
        color: #fff;
        border: 2px solid #0ff1ce;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      .nav-link:hover {
        background: #0ff1ce;
        color: #0a0a1a;
      }
      .game-card {
        background: rgba(10,16,32,0.8);
        border: 1px solid #0ff1ce33;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .specs {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .spec-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 0.25rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #0ff1ce22;
      }
      .spec-label {
        color: #0ff1ce88;
      }
      .scanlines {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
        pointer-events: none;
        background: repeating-linear-gradient(
          to bottom,
          transparent, transparent 6px,
          #0ff1ce08 7px, transparent 8px
        );
        z-index: 10;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden p-8">
    <div class="scanlines"></div>
    <div class="game-card">
      <h1 class="game-hero text-4xl font-black mb-2 text-center">THE WELLSPRING</h1>
      <p class="tagline text-center mb-8">The message was always for you. Now receive it. Now carry it forward.</p>

      <div class="specs">
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Genre</span><span>Narrative Broadcast</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Engine</span><span>Godot 4</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Size</span><span>15.0 MB</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Season</span><span>3</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Character</span><span>Barry Kowalski</span></div>
        <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Price</span><span>Free forever</span></div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        The Wellspring is the last game. Not the biggest — the last. The difference matters.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        You enter the Wellspring — the signal center, the origin point. Barry Kowalski is here. He has been here for four years. He has been waiting. He sits on a lattice strut with his thermos. He has a notebook. He has four years of coffee kept precisely warm.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        He says: "Took you long enough." He says: "I left very clear directions." He says: "The coffee is ready."
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #a0a0b0;">
        The Builders' broadcast resolves into three things: an apology, an invitation, and an introduction. Every choice is the right choice. The game ends the same way regardless. The choice is about you, not the outcome.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-row justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
        <a href="/games/the-wellspring/play/" class="nav-link font-bold">Play Now</a>
        <a href="/games/the-wellspring/about/" class="nav-link">About</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
